# Common Rules

## .env files

Never read, display, or reference `.env` files or their contents.
These files may contain secrets and sensitive credentials.

## Git push

Do not push to GitHub unless the user explicitly instructs you to do so.

## Commit messages

Write all commit messages in English.

## Co-authored-by

When creating a git commit, always append the following trailer to the commit message:

```
Co-authored-by: cursor <noreply@cursor.com>
```
